text: Zhang Yuqian (born 2 May 2000) is a Chinese volleyball player. She played for the Chinese national team. She played at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, 2016 Asian Women's U19 Volleyball Championship, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship. She played for Shanghai women's volleyball team. == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese volleyball players
